Moonlight mead is an unobtainable item intended for use in Construction. It is a variant of Moonlight mead that would have been obtained in a Player-owned house. Players could have obtained it by using an empty beer glass on a Moonlight mead barrel.

For unknown reasons, the Moonlight mead barrel was never added to the game, so the item it produces is unobtainable.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
28 March 2006
(update)

The item was added to the game cache, but was unobtainable.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Uniquely amongst the barrels, a Chef's delight barrel requires 54 Cooking to brew the drink, but only 44 Construction to build it in a player-owned house. Since Moonlight mead requires 44 Cooking to brew, it is likely that Chef's delight took its spot.
